Let me start by saying - do NOT buy this game, not at full price. Default keys setup is absolutely unplayable, you cannot see anything on the screen even if you have a big screen like the HTC One's... You can reposition all buttons, but that's when you get another game, a puzzle game even! You cannot just freely reposition everything the way you'd like it, oh no. You cannot drag ANY button over any other button. 'A' being the biggest and the one you want to use quite a lot can only be positioned to a middle of the screen, because 'B' is blocking its way... After getting somewhat reasonable setup myself, I discovered that I can't play, because 'A' is covered by 'touch D-Pad', so I could only move, but not shot. I know I can do Autofire, but that's more like for kids who never played this game and don't know what is this game like.  I should've get a refund straight away, but unfortunately I downloaded more games which were FREE and WAAAAAAAAYYYYYYY more fun than this silly product. I can imagine the developers say to themselves in their heads 'Oh boy this game is terrible, what have we done...'
